<div class="modal-header">
  <h5 class="modal-title text-danger" id="verifyLabel">Couldn't Verify <%= character.name %></h5>
  <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
  <p>
    XIVAuth was unable to verify <%= character.name %> because that character is currently hidden from anonymous users.
  </p>
  <p>
    Please navigate to the
    <a href="https://<%= registration.extra_data.fetch(:region, "na") %>.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/my/setting/account/" target="_blank">Character Privacy Settings</a> page and
    ensure that the <em>Character Profile Page</em> setting is set to <em>All Users</em>. The character may be hidden
    again after verification is completed.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer">
  <div class="me-auto">
    <div class="text-secondary very-small align-middle">
      Job ID: <span class="font-monospace"><%= job.job_id %></span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">Rats.</button>
</div>